data.description: Are you in the market for a luxurious, spacious home that is practically brand new? Look no further than 40 Landon Ct! This beautiful one-year-old home has four bedrooms and three and a half bathrooms. It sits on a full-acre private cul-de-sac lot with a fenced yard. The location provides a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life.    You'll love the heart of the home, an open-concept gourmet kitchen complete with high-end stainless steel appliances, white cabinets, granite counters, and a large island providing the perfect setting to prepare delicious meals and entertain guests with a breakfast area. Enjoy the soaring two-story great room, complete with a wood-burning fireplace and a wall of windows, overlooking a private fenced yard and natural wooded buffer, which adds to the overall grandeur of this luxury home. Enjoy a large separate dining room that can seat up to 12. The primary bedroom suite is conveniently located on the main floor. It includes a spacious walk-in closet and a luxurious spa bathroom with double vanity sinks, a separate soaking tub, and a walk-in tile shower.     Upstairs, you'll find three more oversized additional bedrooms, two full baths, and a bonus room over the garage - perfect for a home office or playroom. And don't forget the full unfinished daylight basement, which is stubbed for a bathroom and ready for your personal touch. With all of these features and incredible value, this is a home you won't want to miss! Schedule your viewing today!
